<bibRefCitation id="FB514684FFE6E87FFCF8E5F4FC11A79C" author="MEDVEDEV L. N." box="[830,1023,997,1021]" pageId="22" pageNumber="425" pagination="211 - 263" refId="ref13952" refString="MEDVEDEV L. N. 1996: The Chrysomelidae of Arabia. Fauna of Saudi Arabia 15: 211 - 263." type="journal article" year="1996">MEDVEDEV (1996)</bibRefCitation>
