</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="D7DA68FEFFE6E87FFF51E215FC1EA01C" pageId="22" pageNumber="425" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="9F7F3B75FFE6E87FFF51E215FC1EA01C" blockId="22.[151,1127,996,1149]" pageId="22" pageNumber="425">
<emphasis id="ADB4E767FFE6E87FFF51E215FEF8A07D" bold="true" box="[151,278,1028,1052]" pageId="22" pageNumber="425">Comments.</emphasis>
Generic position of this species is unclear. In the Catalogue of Palearctic 
<taxonomicName id="58C040F6FFE6E87FFC29E214FEC1A05C" authority=", BEENEN (2010)" authorityName=", BEENEN" authorityYear="2010" class="Magnoliopsida" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Coleoptera" pageId="22" pageNumber="425" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="order">Coleoptera, BEENEN (2010)</taxonomicName>
followed opinions by 
<bibRefCitation id="FB514684FFE6E87FFDD3E234FD52A05D" author="BECHYNE J." box="[533,700,1060,1084]" pageId="22" pageNumber="425" pagination="478 - 706" refId="ref13212" refString="BECHYNE J. 1958: Notizen zu den neotropischen Chrysomeloidea (Col. Phytophaga). Entomologische Arbeiten aus dem Museum Frey 9: 478 - 706." type="journal article" year="1958">BECHYNĚ (1958)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="FB514684FFE6E87FFD2DE234FC69A05C" author="WILCOX J. A." box="[747,903,1061,1085]" pageId="22" pageNumber="425" pagination="433 - 664" refId="ref14507" refString="WILCOX J. A. 1973: Chrysomelidae: Galerucinae (Luperini: Luperina). In: WILCOX J. A. (ed.): Coleopterorum Catalogus Supplementa. Pars 78 (3). Second edition. W. Junk, ' s-Gravenhage, pp. 433 - 664." type="book chapter" year="1973">WILCOX (1973)</bibRefCitation>
who both classified it in the genus 
<taxonomicName id="58C040F6FFE6E87FFEDEE257FDDDA03D" authority="Bechyne, 1958" authorityName="Bechyne" authorityYear="1958" box="[280,563,1092,1117]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Leptomona" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="22" pageNumber="425" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="ADB4E767FFE6E87FFEDEE257FE60A03C" box="[280,398,1094,1117]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="425">Leptomona</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="FB514684FFE6E87FFE55E254FDDDA03D" author="BECHYNE J." box="[403,563,1092,1117]" pageId="22" pageNumber="425" pagination="478 - 706" refId="ref13212" refString="BECHYNE J. 1958: Notizen zu den neotropischen Chrysomeloidea (Col. Phytophaga). Entomologische Arbeiten aus dem Museum Frey 9: 478 - 706." type="journal article" year="1958">Bechyně, 1958</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="FB514684FFE6E87FFDFDE254FCA1A03C" author="SCHLICH C. &amp; WAGNER T." box="[571,847,1093,1117]" pageId="22" pageNumber="425" pagination="307 - 322" refId="ref14053" refString="SCHLICH C. &amp; WAGNER T. 2010: Species of Monolepta Chevrolat, 1836 from the Arabian Peninsula (Coleoptera, Chrysomelidae, Galerucinae). Entomologica Basiliensia et Collectionis Frey 32: 307 - 322." type="journal article" year="2010">SCHLICH &amp; WAGNER (2010)</bibRefCitation>
excluded it from the genus 
<taxonomicName id="58C040F6FFE6E87FFF51E277FEE6A01C" authorityName="Chevrolat" authorityYear="1836" box="[151,264,1126,1149]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Monolepta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="22" pageNumber="425" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="ADB4E767FFE6E87FFF51E277FEE6A01C" box="[151,264,1126,1149]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="425">Monolepta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with a notice that the correct generic placement will be published later.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
